#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:49
msgid "History length"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:39
msgid ""
"The *history length* saves the last password hashes. These passwords can "
"then not be used by the user as a new password when setting a new "
"password. With a password history length of five, for example, five new "
"passwords must be set before a password can be reused. If no password "
"history check should be performed, the value must be set to ``0``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:45
msgid ""
"The passwords are not stored retroactively. Example: If ten passwords "
"were stored, and the value is reduced to three, the oldest seven "
"passwords will be deleted during the next password change. If then the "
"value is increased again, the number of stored passwords initially "
"remains at three, and is only increased by each password change."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:64
#: ../../user-management/password-settings-windows-clients.rst:24
msgid "Password length"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:52
msgid ""
"The *password length* is the minimum length in characters that a user "
"password must comply with. If no value is entered here, the minimum size "
"is eight characters. The default value of eight characters for password "
"length is fixed, so it always applies if no policy is set and the "
"*Override password check* checkbox is not ticked. This means it even "
"applies if the *default-settings* password policy has been deleted."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:59
msgid ""
"If no password length check should be performed, the value must be set to"
" ``0``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:61
msgid ""
"A per server default can be configured via |UCSUCRV| "
":envvar:`password/quality/length/min`, which applies to users that are "
"not subject to a *UDM password policy*. See the |UCSUCRV| description for"
" details."
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:72
msgid "Password expiry interval"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user-management/password-management.rst:67
msgid ""
